		</div>
		<div class="check-pincode row">
			<div class="col-xs-3" style="padding-left:0 !important; padding-right:0 !important;">
				<div class="title">주문번호</div>
				<div class="amount"><%=ORDERNO%></div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-xs-3" style="padding-left:0 !important; padding-right:0 !important;">
				<div class="title">주문일</div>
				<div class="amount"></div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-xs-3" style="padding-left:0 !important; padding-right:0 !important;">
				<div class="title">주문 금액</div>
				<div class="amount"><%=AMOUNT%></div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-xs-3" style="padding-left:0 !important; padding-right:0 !important;">
				<div class="title">결제 현황</div>
				<div class="amount">완료</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!--div class="way" align="left">
			<p>※ 구매내역 확인 방법</p>
			<p>회원 구매시 : >></p>
			<p>비회원 구매시 : >></p>
		</div-->
		
		<div id="pur-form" align="left">

			<form method="post" action="/finbook_ch_code/<%=ORDERNO%>" name="getcode">
			<input type="hidden" name="">
			<input type="hidden" name="ORDERNO" value="<%=ORDERNO%>">
			<div class="form-box">
				<div class="row form-style1">
					<div class="col-xs-12"><p class="care"> * 결제 완료 후 반드시 신청서를 작성하셔야 진행이 가능합니다.<br>* 각 항목을 빠짐없이 정확하게 입력주세요.</p>
					<div class="col-xs-12"><p class="title">신청자 성명<span class="star"> * </span></p> : <input class="input-style1" type=text name=USERNAME value=""></div>
					<div class="col-xs-12"><p class="title">이메일<span class="star"> * </span></p> : <input class="input-style1" type=text name=EMAIL size=20 value="" placeholder="예) cider@cider.com"></div>
					<div class="col-xs-12"><p class="title">휴대번호<span class="star"> * </span></p> : <input class="input-style1" type="text" name="TELNO" size="" maxlength="11" value="" placeholder="'-', 공백없이"><br><p style="margin-left:116px;">예) 01012345678</p></div>
					<div class="col-xs-12"><p class="title">생년월일</p> : <input class="input-style1" type=text name=USERNAME value="" placeholder="19890101"></div>
					<div class="col-xs-12"><p class="title">성별</p> : 
						<label class="radio-inline" style="margin-left: 10px;">
					      <input type="radio" name="optradio">남
					    </label>
					    <label class="radio-inline">
					      <input type="radio" name="optradio">여
					    </label>
					</div>

					<div class="divider"></div>
					<!--div class="col-xs-12" align="right" class="fincode-btn" onClick="getCode()"><b>핀코드 발급 받기</b></div-->
					<div class="col-xs-12" align="right"><input class="MyButton" type="button" value="신청서 작성완료"  onClick="getCode()" /></div>
				</div>


				
			</div>

